items.title: Swiggy and McDonald's Join Hands to Launch the revolutionary McDonald's Protein Plus Burgers exclusively on the Swiggy app
items.description: Swiggy Limited (NSE: SWIGGY / BSE: 544285), India's leading on-demand convenience platform, today announced that it has partnered with McDonald's India (W&S), to launch its Protein Plus Range of Burgers available exclusively on the Swiggy app, from July 24 to August 11, 2025. Customers can order from this healthier range of their favorite burgers by visiting the 'High Protein' section of the Swiggy app. The range will be available to Swiggy users in 58 cities across Western and Southern India in
